                             names pnetcdf
                             hints ${pnetcdf_dir}
                             path_suffixes "lib" "lib"
                             no_default_path)

                             names cgns
                             hints ${cgns_dir}
                             path_suffixes "lib" "lib"
                             no_default_path)

                             names netcdf
                             hints ${netcdf_dir}
                             path_suffixes "lib" "lib"
                             no_default_path)

                       paths ${netcdf_dir}/bin ${netcdf_bin_dir}
                       no_default_path
                       no_cmake_system_path
                       doc "netcdf configuration script")
